About

Frontend Developer with passion in UX/UI design.

I'm Pat, a frontend developer based in Bangkok, Thailand. I'm 25 years old and graduated from University of Birmingham, UK back in 2020 with a Computer science degree. During the last year of my university I was introduced to UX/UI design in Human Computer Interaction course which is when I become so interested in them that I took extra courses to learn how I can improve my future projects. That interest then soon turn into something I deeply care about as I do believe that if the product is to be made truly for users, then they have to be made with the users in mind.

I'm currently working at BSG group as an IT maintenance where I make sure all devices are operating smoothly (to explain it shortly).
